            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>A feared, lone-wolf-type delinquent.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [771 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a> has released a new trailer for action RPG <em><a title="Games > Kyoto Xanadu [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/kyoto-xanadu">Kyoto Xanadu</a></em> introducing character Kazuki Nakiri (voiced by Ryouta Suzuki). <span id="more-1053619"></span></p><p>Here is his character description, via our <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2026/02/kyoto-xanadu-announced-for-ps5-switch-2-switch-and-pc">previous coverage</a>:</p><blockquote><p>A feared, lone-wolf-type delinquent at Hirasaka Academy.</p><p>He battles in the labyrinth to let off his ferocious, destructive impulses, but when it comes to protecting his younger sister Sena, he will not hesitate to use violence, even against other humans.</p><p>Though he comes across as reckless, he is intelligent and often chooses the strategic when running through the labyrinth.</p></blockquote><p><em>Kyoto Xanadu</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4449410/KYOTO_XANADU_the_Blooming_Phantom/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on July 16 in Japan and Asia. A western release is also planned.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Kazuki Nakiri</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【百鬼千騎 (カズキ)】キャラクタームービー #亰都ザナドゥ" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HOXuVz3Uf7k?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe title="캐릭터 소개 「나키리 카즈키」" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cAsKlvVQnq8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe title="角色介紹「百鬼千騎」" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xw3Ah00wNbY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Simplified Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="角色介绍“百鬼千骑”" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/p95YHXv8wQU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/kyoto-xanadu-character-trailer-kazuki-nakiri]]></content:encoded>
